'''''白色巨塔 The Hospital''''' (''báisè jù tǎ'' in [[pinyin]]— "The Great White Tower", ''The Hospital'' in [[English language|English]] is a [[Taiwanese drama]] produced by the group Yang Ming Production.  The series, with thirty-nine 60-minute episodes (including commericials) made its début on [[August 15|15 August]] [[2006]] on [[China Television]] (CTV).  Its scenario is an adaptation of the same book written by Taiwanese author Hou Wen Yong.

There is a similar [[French-language]] TV series, [[H (French TV series)|H]], broadcast in [[France]] on [[Canal+]] and in [[Canada]] on [[TV5]].[http://www.tv5.ca/television/H.html]

